metadata.name: A Glitch in Time (Collector’s Edition)
metadata.description: PUNKS Comic Issue #3: Just as it seemed life couldn’t get any crazier, the PUNKS find themselves thrust through strange portals into another world full of super-powered humans, including augmented versions of familiar faces! If GFunk, Courtney and crew are to make it back to Origin City alive, they may just have to find a way to take on super, augmented attributes themselves, and risk chancing that these “Glitch Portals” will return them to the right location.
